Clickjacking - Facking a part of original application and capturing his actions

Attack - Get the user's username and password.

	1) Mimic or Forge the design(part of original application)
	         - Login page.
	2) Create an application to capture username and password and send to gmail.
	3) Using iframes to keep as layer.
	
Defence
	Use filter to add 'X-Frame-Options: DENY' for response page. 
	
	This option blocks any site from framing the web page you are trying to protect.